        "subject": "LU-18617 ldiskfs: restore el8.10 before [4.18.0-553.22.1.el8_10]",
        "message": "LU-18617 ldiskfs: restore el8.10 before [4.18.0-553.22.1.el8_10]\n\n4.18.0-553.22.1.el8_10 includes an ext4 fix for which a common\nversion of rhel8.10/ext4-delayed-iput.patch is not possible.\n\nInstead we have to provide a fallback series which uses the former\nbase/ext4-delayed-iput.patch.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial fstype=ldiskfs mdtcount=4 mdscount=2 \\\n  clientdistro=el8.10 serverdistro=el8.10 testlist=sanity\n\nTest-Parameters: optional fstype=zfs mdtcount=4 mdscount=2 \\\n  env=SANITY_EXCEPT=\"66 413\" \\\n  clientdistro=el8.10 serverdistro=el8.10 testlist=sanity\n\nFixes: 40b69da398a (\"LU-18423 kernel: update RHEL 8.10 [4.18.0-553.27.1.el8_10]\")\nChange-Id: Ie746da39760b971e557c9678504e018453754cf3\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <yujian@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
